- `images/service_icon_corp.png`: Icon for Corporate Tax.
- `images/service_icon_inherit.png`: Icon for Inheritance.
- `images/service_icon_startup.png`: Icon for Startup.
- `images/user_icon_m.png`: Male avatar for testimonials.
- `images/user_icon_f.png`: Female avatar for testimonials.
