- **Section Backgrounds**: Ensure alternating backgrounds (`#FFFFFF` and `#F4F4F2`) starting from the Service section.
- **Service Section**: Style as cards with icons centered.
- **Testimonials**: Style as "SWELL" speech bubbles (icon on side, bubble with tail).

### HTML ([index.html](file:///c:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/sakakibara-tax01/index.html))
